{"TopicId":195760,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"How Would You Do Superiority Adaptation As a Movie","CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-21T00:13:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-21T00:13:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nArthur C. Clarke\u0027s short story (little over a page long)\u00A0I found both entertaining and funny.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.mayofamily.com/RLM/txt_Clarke_Superiority.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.mayofamily.com/RLM/txt_Clarke_Superiority.html\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow would you could make a good movie adaptation?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow would movie be if one of these did it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nZack Snyder?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMichael Bay (cringe)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJames Cameron?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSteven Spielburg?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuebtin Tarantino?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I did it, I\u00A0would play it kind of like a tragi-comedy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTragedy being all the mistakes that lead to a final orbital last stand above the homeworld with music similar to this playing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/IX6rHEMYZvU?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComedy being characters thrown in to give the destined-to-lose general company, not unlike the lower decks well received TNG episode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the main character general would be this guy... only with MAXIMUM HAM!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook up tv tropes if you don\u0027t know what \u0027ham\u0027 is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022la-1487361005-kzxrybfvn0-snap-photo\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.31\u0022 height=\u0022473\u0022 width=\u0022840\u0022 src=\u0022https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/1c815d3/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2048x1152\u002B0\u002B0/resize/840x473!/quality/90/?url=https://california-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com/c2/f9/7635229409d65f508c014a3a8be6/la-1487361005-kzxrybfvn0-snap-photo\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-07-21T00:15:13Z\u0022 title=\u002207/21/2020 12:15  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 21, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Spacescifi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-21T07:15:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPentagon Wars (1998).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-21T07:23:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlways bet on Asylum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-22T15:27:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReminds me of \u0022Brazil\u0022 by Terry Gilliam - a dark, dystopic, high-technology future where the main enemy is...poor adminsitration.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}